---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '23 April 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy | Beyond Border Group"
  description="How Beyond Border Group uses cookies and similar technologies on its website. Types of cookies, third-party providers, and how to manage them."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="legal-hero__title">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-hero__meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      <p class="legal-hero__lead">
        Beyond Border Group, operated by BeyondBorderGroup LTD (Hong Kong SAR), uses cookies and
        similar technologies on this website. By continuing to browse our site, you consent to
        the use of cookies as described in this policy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section legal-body">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="prose">
        <h2>What are cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device (computer, tablet or
          mobile phone) when you visit a website. They allow the site to recognise your device
          and remember information about your visit, such as your preferred language or other
          settings.
        </p>

        <h2>How we use cookies</h2>

        <h3>Strictly necessary cookies</h3>
        <p>
          These cookies are essential for the website to function. They enable core features
          such as page navigation, secure access to protected areas, and form submissions. The
          site cannot function properly without these cookies.
        </p>

        <h3>Functional cookies</h3>
        <p>
          These allow the website to remember choices you make, such as your language or
          region, to provide a more personalised experience. Some functional cookies may be
          set by third-party providers whose services appear on our pages.
        </p>

        <h3>Analytics cookies</h3>
        <p>
          We use privacy-focused analytics tools to understand how visitors interact with our
          website, so we can improve it. We do not use Google Analytics, because Google services
          are not reliably accessible from mainland China, a market we serve every day.
        </p>

        <h2>Marketing cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We do not currently use marketing or advertising cookies. If this changes, we will
          update this policy and, where required, ask for your consent.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-party cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Some pages may include content or tools from third-party services which set their own
          cookies. We have no control over cookies set by third parties. We recommend reviewing
          the privacy and cookie policies of those services directly.
        </p>

        <h2>Managing cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Most browsers let you view, delete and block cookies through their settings. You can
          usually find these options under "Privacy" or "Security" in your browser's preferences.
          Please note that disabling some cookies may affect how parts of this website work for
          you.
        </p>

        <h2>Legal framework</h2>
        <p>
          Our use of cookies complies with the laws of the Hong Kong Special Administrative
          Region, in particular the Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. The revised version will be posted
          on this page with an updated date.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about our use of cookies, email
          <a href="mailto:hello@beyondbordergroup.com">hello@beyondbordergroup.com</a>
          or use our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    background: var(--bbg-surface);
    padding: var(--space-7) 0 var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bbg-border);
  }
  .legal-hero .container > * { max-width: 760px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .legal-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw + 1rem, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--bbg-ink);
    margin: var(--space-3) auto var(--space-3);
  }
  .legal-hero__meta {
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--bbg-text-muted);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-5);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .legal-hero__lead {
    font-size: var(--fs-lead);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--bbg-text);
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal-body { padding-top: var(--space-7); padding-bottom: var(--space-7); }

  .prose {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--bbg-text);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bbg-ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: var(--space-7) 0 var(--space-3);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .prose h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bbg-ink);
    margin: var(--space-5) 0 var(--space-2);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 var(--space-4); }
  .prose ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .prose a { color: var(--bbg-blue); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--bbg-blue-dark); }
</style>
